    },
    "Management": {
      "text": "Treat underlying illness, if known\nManage critical complications: see treatment section of\ndiffuse alveolar hemorrhage\n,\nacute limb ischemia\n,\nKawasaki\nFor primary vasculitides, this will likely involve an immunosuppressive agent, such as:\nPrednisone\n/\nMethylprednisolone\nCyclophosphamide\n,\nmethotrexate\n,\nazathioprine\nRituximab\nMay consider\nplasmapheresis\nfor severe or rapidly progressive",
